plan_decisions[1]{ts,author,decision,rationale}:
  "2026-05-22T21:11:00.067Z",claude-code-agent,"Re-anchor in raw replay space, not via createHistoryEntry","Keep clean entries' patches verbatim (minimal diff) and recompute only hashes; lenient-repair only entries that no longer strictly apply; append a reconciliation entry compare(finalReplay,currentItem) so the latest after_hash equals validate/health's hashDocument(currentItem). Computing in raw replay space (not canonical createHistoryEntry) guarantees verifyHistoryChain passes without canonicalization drift."
plan_discoveries[1]{ts,author,text}:
  "2026-05-22T21:11:00.328Z",claude-code-agent,"pm-lty: a legacy stream whose first entry is a partial update (not a create) replays to a non-canonicalizable doc, so replayHash threw. Fix: replayHash falls back to a deterministic structural hash for such states; fully formed docs are unaffected and stay consistent with validate."
